sentences: Hans Dulfer (born 28 May 1940) is a Dutch jazz musician who plays tenor saxophone.
Hans Dulfer was born on 28 May 1940 in Amsterdam, Netherlands.
He has comparatively high popularity in Japan where Hyperbeat was a top-selling CD by instrumental standards.
